title: Make Way for Love
lyrics:
Make way for love
Make way for love
When, by design
You are on your knees
I'm no wealth comfort

To afford you



Then

Shall the wonder

Of the ages

Be revealed again



Make way for love

Only for you

Leading you on

All through the night



Only for love

Deep as the ocean

Here is the will

Here is way, the way in to love



Oh, let

The wonder

Of the ages

Be reveal-less love
